{"tid":1624524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵一次私了洗劫者,再拍晒片煲大佢就得","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:47:21.000Z","uid":95520,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec59504d4a7c9f71fa370625876c90314a24a91","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:05.000Z","msg":"你哋咪撚咁on9啦<br />\n政府出招搵人洗劫抹黑你就停晒啲嘢<br />\n政府搵人遊行搞事你又唔停埋遊行?<br />\n<br />\n講到尾都係公關戰文宣戰<br />\n最好下次就有人洗劫,然後成班手足去私了佢<br />\n比傳媒影晒<br />\n再公開表明洗劫者並不是示威者,強烈譴責<br />\n<br />\n咁道德光環你咪拎返晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做一次半次之後政府呢招就徹底廢咗<br />\n<br />\n政府出招時可唔可以學識將計就計<br />\n而唔係斬腳趾避沙蟲"},{"pid":"bff7f63aeebbf88e48da4992a0f8e652cd578221","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"醒少少"},{"pid":"b3f70903cfbcd4a963b74a292c509864009a766d","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"032a65973f4983f6ce35bb37c0e4b77e411da2e1","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"正經post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲縮沙風向post就成班推<br />\n食屎啦"},{"pid":"bd710a4236be5832fe674af6ddd8f9609707e062","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人想回應吓<br />\n或者幫推都好啊"},{"pid":"f37d2e3dcdb87ec44900fac95c5e3baa71f1e5dd","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"7bb738e7bd9b0c684162d03fefafa6c298f6f029","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46f0842ada2d4d2e2ae24c07a72aebe38efadb21","tid":1624524,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:28.000Z","msg":